Package Hospital.Argument

Interface Summary
Argument<T> This class holds the answer to some information that is needed.
PublicArgument<T> Public arguments contain a method to parse the string put in by the user.
 

Class Summary
BasicArgument<T> A BasicArgument has a question to ask the user, the answer of which must be able to be parsed to a given type.
BooleanArgument Boolean version of Public Argument, used to ask a boolean value of the user.
DiagnosisArgument This class supports the adding of a Diagnosis to the argumentList Care should be taken that this arguments doesn't get exposed.
DoctorArgument This class supports the adding of a Doctor to the argumentList Care should be taken that this argument doesn't get exposed.
IntegerArgument Integer version of Public Argument, used to ask an integer value of the user.
ItemArgument This class supports the adding of a item to the argumentList Care should be taken that this argument doesn't get exposed.
StringArgument String version of Public Argument, used to ask a String of the user.
TimeArgument Time version of Public Argument, used to ask a Time of the user.
